data.description: Incredible 5 bedroom 2 bath with detached 2 car garage and huge storage shed for space and comfort.  Easy access to highways, schools and parks.  This home has sprinklers in front and back for easy maintenance.  Double pain windows, hardwood floors, carpet and tile.  Long concrete driveway that can accommodate at least another 6 vehicles or RV.  Nice clean tile in the basement, laundry room and standup shower for the 2 bedrooms downstairs.  This is a very large lot for entertaining guest in the summer months. The A/C is a bonus and one less thing to worry about.
